body:
### Failstacks

Use cheap accessories to get to **2** failstacks.
Use cheap PRI accessories to get to **5** failstacks.
Use green armor to get to the desired number of failstacks.

**Going for +15 Liverto or Kzarka?**

> * +8 = 4 Stacks
> * +9 = 7 stacks
> * +10 = 10 stacks
> * +11 = 10 stacks
> * +12 = 18 stacks
> * +13 = 20 stacks
> * +14 = 25 stacks
> * +15 = 25 stacks

**Going for +15 Boss Armor?**

> * +6 = 4 Stacks
> * +7 = 7 stacks
> * +8 = 10 Stacks
> * +9 = 12 stacks
> * +10 = 14 stacks
> * +11 = 16 stacks
> * +12 = 18 stacks
> * +13 = 20 stacks
> * +14 = 25 stacks
> * +15 = 25 stacks
